Great trip!!
Captivating scenic landscapes awaited us, though December brought chilly winds. Opting for a day trip, our family, each at USD60, arranged through our hotel, experienced a seamless journey with an 8 am hotel pickup and an 8:30 pm return. The coach ride from Hoan Kiem to Ha Long took approximately 2 hours and 30 minutes. The Ha Long Bay cruise, including a buffet, spanned 1 hour and 30 minutes, featuring the Surprising Cave as the first stop. A 15 to 20-minute speed boat ride (additional cost of 240K dong each) followed, complementing the bamboo boat, included in the day trip package. The adventure continued with the exploration of Ti Top Cave before returning to the port.
